Onyeka Azike (amụrụ na Julaị 1, 1990) bụ onye Naijiria na-ebu ibu

O sonyere na 2006 Commonwealth Games, merie ọlaọcha na nkewa ụmụ nwanyị 53 kilogram na 2006 Commonwealth Olympics na Melbourne, Australia, wee merie ọla edo na 58 kilogram na-ebe ibu usuro na usoro  nke 2007 All Africa Games na Algeria.
